        <para id="id6339119">1. How can an individual teacher strengthen his professional organizations?</para>
        <para id="id10746296">2. What different methods are there of preventing discipline problems from arising? Can certain discipline problems be anticipated?</para>
        <para id="id10707296">3. Do teachers' unions differ from professional associations? If so, how?</para>
      </section>
